---
title: Falafel and Veggie 'Nduja Wraps with Yoghurt Sauce, Greek Style Cheese, Baby Gem Salad and Chips
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, these tasty Falafel and Veggie 'Nduja Wraps are perfect for a casual sharing-style vegetarian dinner.
